The paper focuses on clustering, which is a fundamental task in machine learning and data analysis. The proposed method involves optimizing an auto-encoder with a discriminative pairwise loss function during the pre-training phase. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), and computational linguistics (cs.CL).
